name: FreshBru
overview:
Howdy, and welcome to FreshBru. Wondering who we are? Well you’ve come to the right place. We are an affiliated group of talented designers, illustrators, marketers, and developers who produce high-quality work without the big-name corporate run-around. We each have our own respective clientele but combine forces to provide our clients with the most effective results.

In September of 2011 the key playing members that make up the FreshBru Collective planted a seed that over the next few months would grow to its true potential. With our combined expertise and wide spectrum of industry experience we not only are able to offer top of the line design and marketing services but due to high demand are now proud to offer our expertise in professional resume services.
